<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/profile.css">
    <title>My Profile</title>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="wrapper">
        <header>
                <a href="/index" class="logoIndex"><img src="img/tempLogo.svg" class="svg"></a>
        </header>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="backgroundBox">
                <div class="profileHeader">
                    <div id="profilePic"></div>
                    <div class="profileHeaderText">
                        <p class="pHT1">{{user.first_name}} {{user.last_name}}</p>
                        <p class="pHT2"><img src="/img/location.svg" class="locationIcon">{{user.city}}, {{user.country}}</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="profileIcons"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="profileContent"> 
                    <div class="profileMusicSheets profileContentBoxes"></div>
                    <div class="profileAbout profileContentBoxes">
                        <p class="profileGroupsText">About</p>
                        <div class="profileAboutWrapper">
                            <div class="profileAboutItem">
                                <img src="/img/musicNote.svg" class="profileAboutIcon">
                                <p class="aboutItemTitle">{{user.instrument}}</p>
                            </div>
                            <p class="aboutText">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consetetur sadipscing elitr, sed diam nonumy eirmod tempor invidunt ut labore et dolore magna aliquyam erat, sed diam voluptua. At vero eos et accusam et justo duo dolores et ea rebum. Stet clita kasd gubergren, no sea takimata sanctus est Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet. </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="profileGroups profileContentBoxes">
                        <p class="profileGroupsText">Groups / Bands</p>
                        <div class="profileGroupsWrapper">
                            <div class="profileGroup">
                                <div class="profileGroupImage group1"></div>
                                <p class="profileGroupTitle">Bielefelder Orchester</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="profileGroup">
                                <div class="profileGroupImage group2"></div>
                                <p class="profileGroupTitle">Placeholder Band</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="profileGroup">
                                <div class="profileGroupImage group2"></div>
                                <p class="profileGroupTitle">Placeholder Band</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>